OL,3,CStrikes from New Year's Eve across
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast railway lines
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FStrike action has been announced by
OL,8,Fthe RMT union from New Year's Eve, set
OL,9,Fto cause delays and disruption for
OL,10,Fmonths into 2025.
OL,12,FAvanti West Coast services will be
OL,13,Fimpacted, with the operator announcing
OL,14,Fthis evening that the strikes will
OL,15,Ftake place after failing to agree on a
OL,16,Fdeal with the RMT.
OL,18,FAvanti has described their pay offer
OL,19,Fas very reasonable and said that they
OL,20,Fare disappointed with the train
OL,21,Fmanagers who declined their offer.
