OL,3,CStrikes from New Year's Eve across
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast railway lines
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe RMT union will strike on 31
OL,8,FDecember and 2 January. They will also
OL,9,Fbe striking every Sunday from 12
OL,10,FJanuary to 25 May 2025.
OL,12,FAvanti West Coast has said this strike
OL,13,Faction will cause significant
OL,14,Fdisruption to our customers making
OL,15,Fjourneys on the West Coast Main Line
OL,16,Fover an extended period.
