OL,3,CStrikes from New Year's Eve across
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast railway lines
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "We're
OL,8,Fdisappointed our Train Managers who
OL,9,Fare RMT members have voted to decline
OL,10,Fthe very reasonable revised offer made
OL,11,Fto them to resolve the Rest Day
OL,12,FWorking dispute and avoid
OL,13,Finconveniencing our customers. We
OL,14,Fremain open to working with the RMT to
OL,15,Fresolve the dispute."
OL,17,FA Department for Transport
OL,18,Fspokesperson said:
