OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"This is incredibly disappointing news
OL,8,Ffor passengers who would have been
OL,9,Fhoping to leave strike action in 2024,
OL,10,Fand we strongly encourage both the RMT
OL,11,Fand Avanti West Coast to get back
OL,12,Faround the table and work in good
OL,13,Ffaith to resolve this as quickly as
OL,14,Fpossible.
