OL,3,CStrikes from New Year's Eve across
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast railway lines
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"As part of our plans to reform the
OL,8,Frailways, we're determined to move
OL,9,Ftowards a seven-day working week and
OL,10,Fend the overreliance on rest day
OL,11,Fworking, giving passengers the
OL,12,Fcertainty and reliability they
OL,13,Fdeserve."
OL,15,FThe National Union of Rail, Maritime
OL,16,Fand Transport Workers (RMT) had
OL,17,Fpreviously agreed to strike on 22,23,
OL,18,Fand 29 December, but suspended strike
OL,19,Faction after receiving a new offer
OL,20,Ffrom Avanti West Coast.
