OL,3,CStrikes from New Year's Eve across
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast railway lines
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FHowever, following a vote on the offer
OL,8,Fon Tuesday 17 December strikes are now
OL,9,Fset to return at the end of the month.
OL,11,FRest Day Working payments and
OL,12,Farrangements over a new technology
OL,13,Fagreement were a couple of the key
OL,14,Ffactors voted on by the RMT.
OL,16,FThe RMT has been contacted for comment.
